00:44:59.268 --> 00:45:03.248
myeloid cells or in the circulation, but it just

752
00:45:04.028 --> 00:45:07.868
will prolong the stability and prolong the

753
00:45:07.888 --> 00:45:08.828
TIF2 MSA

754
00:45:09.928 --> 00:45:13.608
persistence in the circulation and in the body. Yeah.

755
00:45:14.888 --> 00:45:15.308
