1368
01:21:38.711 --> 01:21:40.791
in blue with glioblastoma.

1369
01:21:41.972 --> 01:21:42.221
Then,

1370
01:21:43.432 --> 01:21:47.092
to see if this accumulation of senescence in older

1371
01:21:47.152 --> 01:21:51.092
mice can be reduced, the young and old mice were treated with

1372
01:21:51.112 --> 01:21:52.772
or without the brain radiotherapy.

1373
01:21:53.212 --> 01:21:57.172
